description: Try our easy to follow Tuna Patties + Snacks recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
name: Tuna Patties + Snacks Recipe | Woolworths
recipeIngredient: 185 g can tuna chunks In springwater

recipeInstructions.text: Pack capsicum & cucumber sticks in an airtight container. Serve with tuna patties. Snack 1: Pack pineapple in an airtight container Snack 2: Top muffin with cheese. Grill until cheese is melted. Cool and cut in half.
